    <item>
      <title>LeetCode 33: Search in Rotated Sorted Array</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/leetcode/binary-search/search-rotated-array/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/leetcode/binary-search/search-rotated-array/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;h1&gt;🧩 Question: Search in Rotated Sorted Array (LeetCode 33)&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;A sorted array has been rotated at an unknown pivot. Find &lt;code&gt;target&lt;/code&gt; in $O(\log n)$.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;🎯 What the interviewer is testing&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;-what-the-interviewer-is-testing&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#-what-the-interviewer-is-testing&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Binary search on non-standard sorted structures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Logic for identifying which half is &amp;ldquo;sorted&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Boundary condition handling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;🧠 Deep Explanation&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;-deep-explanation&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#-deep-explanation&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3&gt;The Key Insight:&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;the-key-insight&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#the-key-insight&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;In a rotated sorted array, &lt;strong&gt;one of the two halves split by &lt;code&gt;mid&lt;/code&gt; is always sorted&lt;/strong&gt;. We check which half is sorted, then decide if the target is in that range.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Algorithm:&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;algorithm&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#algorithm&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Calculate &lt;code&gt;mid&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;If &lt;code&gt;nums[low] &amp;lt;= nums[mid]&lt;/code&gt; → left half is sorted.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;If &lt;code&gt;target&lt;/code&gt; in &lt;code&gt;[nums[low], nums[mid])&lt;/code&gt; → shrink right.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Else → shrink left.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Else → right half is sorted.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;If &lt;code&gt;target&lt;/code&gt; in &lt;code&gt;(nums[mid], nums[high]]&lt;/code&gt; → shrink left.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Else → shrink right.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;✅ Ideal Answer&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;-ideal-answer&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#-ideal-answer&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Even a rotated array has at least one monotonically sorted half. We identify it on each iteration and check if the target fits within it, discarding the half where it cannot be.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;💻 Java Code&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;-java-code&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#-java-code&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-block hx-relative hx-mt-6 first:hx-mt-0 hx-group/code&#34;&gt;
  

&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;Solution&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;search&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;[]&lt;/span&gt; nums, &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; target) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; low &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; 0, high &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; nums.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;length&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; 1;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;while&lt;/span&gt; (low &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;=&lt;/span&gt; high) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; mid &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; low &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; (high &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; low) &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; 2;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (nums&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;mid&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; target) &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; mid;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (nums&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;low&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;=&lt;/span&gt; nums&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;mid&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;) { &lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// Left sorted&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (target &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;=&lt;/span&gt; nums&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;low&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; target &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; nums&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;mid&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;) high &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; mid &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; 1;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; low &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; mid &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; 1;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            } &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;// Right sorted&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (target &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; nums&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;mid&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; target &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;lt;=&lt;/span&gt; nums&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;high&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;) low &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; mid &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; 1;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; high &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; mid &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; 1;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;return&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;1;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn-container hx-opacity-0 hx-transition group-hover/code:hx-opacity-100 hx-flex hx-gap-1 hx-absolute hx-m-[11px] hx-right-0 hx-top-0&#34;&gt;
  &lt;button
    class=&#34;hextra-code-copy-btn hx-group/copybtn hx-transition-all active:hx-opacity-50 hx-bg-primary-700/5 hx-border hx-border-black/5 hx-text-gray-600 hover:hx-text-gray-900 hx-rounded-md hx-p-1.5 dark:hx-bg-primary-300/10 dark:hx-border-white/10 dark:hx-text-gray-400 dark:hover:hx-text-gray-50&#34;
    title=&#34;Copy code&#34;
  &gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;copy-icon group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-hidden hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;success-icon hx-hidden group-[.copied]/copybtn:hx-block hx-pointer-events-none hx-h-4 hx-w-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

  
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;🔄 Follow-up Questions&lt;span class=&#34;hx-absolute -hx-mt-20&#34; id=&#34;-follow-up-questions&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a href=&#34;#-follow-up-questions&#34; class=&#34;subheading-anchor&#34; aria-label=&#34;Permalink for this section&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Array with duplicates?&lt;/strong&gt; (LeetCode 81: Worst case degrades to $O(N)$ when &lt;code&gt;nums[low] == nums[mid] == nums[high]&lt;/code&gt;.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Find the rotation pivot?&lt;/strong&gt; (LeetCode 153: Binary search comparing &lt;code&gt;nums[mid]&lt;/code&gt; vs &lt;code&gt;nums[high]&lt;/code&gt;.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Complexity?&lt;/strong&gt; ($O(\log N)$ time, $O(1)$ space.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

